User: Awesome, what's next?

Gemini: ACTION 1.6.42: MONITOR VERTEX AI MODEL DEPLOYMENT STATUS

Please follow these steps in the GOOGLE CLOUD CONSOLE to monitor the status of your Vertex AI Model deployment:

Navigate to VERTEX AI in the GOOGLE CLOUD CONSOLE: https://console.cloud.google.com/vertex-ai (or go back to your Google Cloud Console and navigate to Vertex AI again).

Go to the "MODELS" SECTION in VERTEX AI:

In the LEFT-HAND NAVIGATION MENU, under "DEPLOY AND USE," CLICK on "Model Registry." (or if "Model Registry" is not directly visible, look for a main "Models" section under "Deploy and use" and click on that).
This should take you to the Vertex AI Model Registry page, where you will see a list of your Vertex AI Models.
FIND YOUR "CUSTOM MODEL" in the MODEL REGISTRY LIST:

Look for the "Model Name" you gave to your Custom Model (e.g., custom-ai-execution-model or whatever name you chose). It should be listed in the Model Registry table.
CHECK the "STATUS" or "VERSION STATUS" of your CUSTOM MODEL:

In the Model Registry list, look at the "STATUS" or "VERSION STATUS" column for your Custom Model. (The column name might vary slightly depending on the Vertex AI UI version).
Initially, the status will likely be "Deploying..." "Creating..." "Training..." or similar. This indicates that Vertex AI is currently working on deploying your Custom Model (container).
YOU NEED TO WAIT until the STATUS changes to something that indicates SUCCESSFUL DEPLOYMENT and READINESS, such as:
"Deployed"
"Active"
"Ready"
"Succeeded"
MONITOR the STATUS PERIODICALLY:

REFRESH the Model Registry page periodically (e.g., by clicking the "Refresh" button in your browser or pressing F5) to check for updates to the Model Status.
Deployment can take some time (several minutes or even longer, depending on image size and resource provisioning). Be patient and keep monitoring the status.
CHECK for EMAIL NOTIFICATION (as mentioned in the UI message):

Keep an eye on your EMAIL INBOX associated with your Google Cloud Account. Vertex AI should send you an email notification when the Model deployment is complete. The email might take a few minutes to arrive after the deployment finishes in the console.
Once the "STATUS" of your CUSTOM MODEL in the Vertex AI Model Registry becomes "Deployed," "Active," "Ready," or similar, and/or you receive the EMAIL NOTIFICATION, REPORT BACK "VERTEX AI CUSTOM MODEL DEPLOYED!"

After you report "VERTEX AI CUSTOM MODEL DEPLOYED!", we will then proceed to the ULTIMATE TEST: SENDING a PREDICTION REQUEST to your DEPLOYED ENDPOINT and VERIFYING that your AI Execution System is RUNNING LIVE on VERTEX AI!

Jesse, please execute ACTION 1.6.42 - MONITOR VERTEX AI MODEL DEPLOYMENT STATUS RIGHT NOW! Navigate to the Model Registry, find your Custom Model, and patiently monitor its status until it shows "Deployed" or a similar success status! Let's confirm that deployment is successful and then get ready to TEST!
